For PR, the complexity is increased with respect to polynomial order from 1 to 6, and an optimum polynomial order of 3 is obtained (please refer to Supplementary Fig. 1). For SVM with RBF kernel, two parameters are considered, which are C and gamma (\documentclass[12pt]{minimal}
